-- China to Give Verdict in Bo’s Wife Trial Aug. 20: CNN
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-08-17T04:23:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-17/china-to-give-verdict-in-bo-s-wife-trial-aug-20-cnn-correct-.html
(Corrects date in headline, first paragraph.)  Chinese authorities will announce
the verdict in the trial of the wife of deposed Politburo member
Bo Xilai on Aug. 20,  CNN  reported, citing an unidentified friend
of her family.  The announcement will be made at 9 a.m. local time,
according to the report.  Calls to the news office of the Hefei Intermediate People’s
Court went unanswered.  To contact Bloomberg News staff for this story:
John Liu in Beijing at 
